description:
FNF A.G.O.T.I TEST

This is my try for an FNF TEST game where you can test your favorite character from Friday Night Funkin.

Press the PLAY button and after that, you can start. Choose normal or angry AGOTI and start moving around.

[Friday Night Funkin A.G.O.T.I TEST - WITH INSTRUMENTAL!!!]

If you like this FNF AGOTI TEST game, please leave a reply. In this way, I know that you like my work, and I will make more! :)

If you have any feedback, please leave it here.

When we hit 100 coments I will post the secret combination to see the special move of A.G.O.T.I from image 4!!!
